            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 55.35 50.89"><polygon points="55.35 0 55.35 50.89 36.78 50.89 18.57 25.27 18.57 50.89 0 50.89 0 0 18.57 0 36.78 26.65 36.78 0 55.35 0"/></svg>
          </a>
